<i>We endorse this polo rig, of course</i>

1140
01:25:00,630 --> 01:25:03,761
<i>And for an added 1,000 francs</i>
<i>we furnish horses</i>

1141
01:25:04,630 --> 01:25:08,013
<i>Or if you're doing splits on skis</i>
<i>at St. Moritz</i>

1142
01:25:08,150 --> 01:25:11,314
<i>You'd be the best-dressed</i>
<i>"faller-downer" on the courses</i>

1143
01:25:12,087 --> 01:25:15,982
<i>Now take the dowager who is glad</i>
<i>to leave her watchman for tea</i>

1144
01:25:16,438 --> 01:25:19,853
<i>She'll wear this patriotic plaid</i>
<i>and meet that Scotchman for tea</i>

1145
01:25:20,502 --> 01:25:23,285
<i>When summertime begins</i>
<i>this costume always wins</i>

1146
01:25:23,351 --> 01:25:26,580
<i>When 50 million little Frenchmen</i>
<i>clap their fins</i>

1147
01:25:27,191 --> 01:25:30,507
<i>For hunting grouse or quail</i>
<i>Roberta ran up this suit</i>

1148
01:25:30,710 --> 01:25:34,834
<i>The modest price includes</i>
<i>the bag, the gun and two ducks to shoot</i>

1149
01:25:35,190 --> 01:25:38,038
<i>And should Amelia Earhart care</i>
<i>to get a breath of air</i>

1150
01:25:38,103 --> 01:25:41,452
<i>this is the last thing in the world</i>
<i>she'd ever wear</i>

1151
01:25:46,743 --> 01:25:51,020
- Ladislaw, are we gathering later?
- The Princess begs to be excused.

1152
01:25:51,126 --> 01:25:53,941
We are leaving for Rome
immediately the showing is finished.

1153
01:25:59,158 --> 01:26:00,914
<i>It is the hour for dry martinis</i>

1154
01:26:00,983 --> 01:26:03,470
<i>The park is full of little Fords</i>
<i>and Isotta Fraschinis</i>

1155
01:26:03,542 --> 01:26:05,909
<i>The Ritz bar is serving caviar and weenies</i>

1156
01:26:06,006 --> 01:26:07,380
<i>Madame is there</i>

1157
01:26:07,478 --> 01:26:10,031
<i>And from Roberta she has something</i>
<i>that is too divine on</i>

1158
01:26:10,102 --> 01:26:13,233
<i>The sort of thing your jealous friends</i>
<i>would love to spill their wine on</i>

1159
01:26:13,302 --> 01:26:16,302
<i>For your inspection, our cocktail collection</i>

1160
01:28:32,086 --> 01:28:35,348
<i>Clothes must play a part</i>

1161
01:28:35,446 --> 01:28:38,829
<i>To light an eye, to win a heart</i>

1162
01:28:38,902 --> 01:28:41,455
<i>They say a gown can almost speak</i>

1163
01:28:42,550 --> 01:28:44,939
